label: FOSDEM
name: Free and Open Source Software Developers European Meeting
description:
FOSDEM is a free event for software developers to meet, share ideas and collaborate.

Every year, thousands of developers of free and open source software from all over the world gather at the event in Brussels.

label: FLISOL
name: Festival Latinoamericano de Instalación de Software Libre

label: FOSSA
name: Free and Open Source Software Auditing
description: The next EU-FOSSA 2 Hackathon, on 4/5th May, has broadened its scope. It will still have a large focus on Apache Tomcat, but will now also include other communities under the Apache Software Foundation (ASF). Aditionally, the Hackathon will be offering training sessions on some of the latest ASF projects.

label: GUADEC

label: Das ist Netzpolitik!
name: Das ist Netzpolitik!
description: Die Konferenz: In 24 Stunden wird auf drei Bühnen in der großartigen Volksbühne Berlin und im Anschluss im Mensch Meier ein Rundumschlag über alle relevanten aktuellen Debatten der digitalen Welt stattfinden.
